        </article>
        <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">N&#xE5;v&#xE6;rende kapittel VII blir nytt kapittel VIII.</article>
        <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">N&#xE5;v&#xE6;rende &#xA7; 16 &#x2013; &#xA7; 20 i kapittel VII blir nye &#xA7; 18 &#x2013; &#xA7; 22 i kapittel VIII.</article>
      </section>
